        <obo:IAO_0000115 xml:lang="en">A subbiome of the Temperate-Boreal Grassland and Shrubland biome comprising temperate and boreal cliff and rock outcrop ecosystems characterised by minimal soil development, stress-tolerant vegetation, and high local endemism.</obo:IAO_0000115>
        <obo:IAO_0000116 xml:lang="en">Definition sourced from IUCN Global Ecosystem Typology (https://global-ecosystems.org) and adapted for ontology use.</obo:IAO_0000116>
